The paper deals with the problem of completing online knowledge libraries, which involves information retrieval (IR), artificial intelligence (AI), machine learning (LG), and database (DB) techniques. The paper also involves natural language processing (CL) to some extent, as it deals with movie entities and their attributes. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR, followed by cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB, and cs.CL.
